snippet.title: Star Trek - Strategic Operations Simulator - Arcade Game - My best game ever.
snippet.description: Back in the early 90's, i actually owned one of these full size cabinets. It was a beast, and REALLY heavy. A few years later, it failed, and I left it at my Aunt's house ... until she moved and got rid of it. Anyway, this is the game on MAME ... and this is probably my best high score ever.
